---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy" description="DataIsland Software Privacy Policy">

  <section class="legal fade-in">
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>

    <p>
      DataIsland Software is committed to building privacy‑first tools. Our apps are designed
      to keep your data on your device whenever possible, and we never sell or share your
      personal information.
    </p>

    <h2>Data Collection</h2>
    <p>
      Our applications collect only the minimum information required to operate. Many features
      run entirely on‑device with no cloud processing.
    </p>

    <h2>Local Processing</h2>
    <p>
      Fusion, Check This, and other DataIsland apps prioritize local computation. Your content,
      documents, and email metadata remain on your device unless you explicitly choose to export
      or sync them.
    </p>

    <h2>Website Analytics</h2>
    <p>
      We use lightweight, privacy‑respecting analytics to understand site usage without tracking
      individuals or storing personal identifiers.
    </p>

    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>
      If you have questions about this policy, contact us at:
      <br />
      <strong>support@dataisland.com</strong>
    </p>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .legal {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 3rem 0;
  }

  .legal h1 {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .legal h2 {
    margin-top: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .legal p {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
  }
</style>
